{"tid":1390622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]曾經嘅淺黃港豬老母又變返藍 可以點做","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:55:36.000Z","uid":52898,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"51b42a297827dc578aa465e87cc7caf52bbde365","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"有啲長，但求下大家教我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家母細個經歷毛主席萬歲時代，對共產黨極反感，於是用盡方法就算比人拉左2次都要偷渡去澳門，後來同我呀爸結左婚先黎左香港。<br />\n<br />\n14年嘅時候，佢未至於講出搞亂香港嘅說話，但佢話：「班學生太天真喇，你地唔好咁傻啦，我64都有出去支持，但爭取至啲咩呀？到你地有家庭有負擔嘅時候就唔會講要民主自由，一家人平平安安有飯開咪算好，你地唔好咁天真啦！」<br />\n<br />\n到今次，解釋左送中條例之後佢當然反對啦，佢咁辛苦先逃離共產黨點會想比人捉返上去，見到大家咁辛苦出來遊行、圍警總佢都會多謝大家同時表示好心痛示威者。但佢一直主張：「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同細佬千祈唔好去呢啲地方呀，政治呢啲野唔到我地呢啲小市民理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 」反問佢：「個個都咁諗仲有邊個會出黎？」佢就會話：「呢個世界一定有班人出黎架啦，總之<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地唔好出去啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>」去到元朗、西環之後睇住班狗同黑社會亂打人，佢都依然咬牙切齒咁屌政府。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但岩岩打風早放返到屋企，佢同細佬討論緊琴日不合作運動班港豬嘅時候，家母表示阻住人地搵食，比老細炒好慘架！之後就開始<span style=\"color: red;\">發表偉論話依家有外國勢力加入搞亂香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今日睇醫生個陣都有個呀婆都識講，話本身都好支持示威者，但係去到依家香港已經好亂，你見美國個邊又同中國鬥緊，所以一定係美國有份比錢黎搞亂香港同中國黑吃黑！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你可唔可以唔好咁搞笑，人講咩你信咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你信唔信都好，總之美國一定有比錢叫啲人出黎！我問個呀婆佢都話自己係香港人唔係中國人，一開始都係支持你地架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁依家比$3000你落去比人打你會唔會去？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：政治呢啲野緊係唔到我呢啲小市民理，個呀婆都話去衝立法會個日個啲人係外國勢力(佢意思係梁繼平義士)，佢地搞亂完香港有晒外國護照就走！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：人地去讀書咋，仲有既然你都想去美國又有錢收，不如一齊出去，挖空美國庫房又可以移民！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（開始思緒混亂）人地美國當你係狗咋！我同你老豆咁辛苦先捱大你地，總之你地就咪去呢啲地方！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你都係驚無人養你姐，你都話有外國勢力比錢，我地出多去幾次容乜易就有十萬八萬啦，到時又有美國護照！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：得一部分人有錢收咋（<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），你地唔好咁傻出去比人打，依家香港好亂，總之<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地就唔好去呢啲地方！我地呢啲小市民唔理得咁多，唔好再講政治，唔到我理</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後岩岩佢有個藍絲朋友send左段唔知邊條八婆係度賴中立屌9老師為人師表教到我個仔點點點，又話你地班大學生所謂嘅民主係咪唔比人表達意見？總之我唔理爭取啲乜自由，你地唔好教壞啲心智未成熟嘅年青人，同埋我個仔之類嘅說話，佢一路聽一路笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我應該要點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家先send長輩圖仲有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef608f0a4317878f938db8aabe4ecea4c4101aa","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7269df3aabdddcd920e4929cf86b0e9115a1396","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"21b5bc2ece87233122cec3bb122b093ee068b20d","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"29d428483fb91bca921a2976380539ca3f8fe699","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"光<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"9227df166dc9fc58fcf067b466df2629befc5544","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29d428483fb91bca921a2976380539ca3f8fe699","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"光<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"6d4cdff1a3e4dd6210398690475419fe2e2914e9","tid":1390622,"uid":138296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"應該係冇咩思考能力 係咁洗佢腦 cut tvb"},{"pid":"ab8a7be66bb682fb307b0694badacfbb72dbb3f5","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9227df166dc9fc58fcf067b466df2629befc5544","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29d428483fb91bca921a2976380539ca3f8fe699","tid":1390622,"uid":52898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019